    "description": "BetaScan2 is a statistics suite. BetaScan2 can calculate \u03b2std on a predefined window of interest, instead of requiring the use of a sliding window across the genome. This locus-based calculation is made possible by standardization allowing comparison of scores across different window sizes, and enables the use of \u03b2 on species for which only a small fraction of the genome is available.",
